129
00:06:35,608 --> 00:06:36,615
Attends.

130
00:06:37,172 --> 00:06:38,310
Et Maman ?

131
00:06:38,394 --> 00:06:40,680
Maman va à l'inauguration
de la galerie de Tante Quinn,

132
00:06:40,763 --> 00:06:42,866
